spec/classes/nova_db_spec.rb.message:
I think we can just simplify these test cases like the following example.

~~~
    it { should_not contain_oslo__db('nova_config') }
    it { should_not contain_oslo__db('api_database') }
~~~

It's better to test the implementation of oslo::db here since it makes it difficult to update oslo::db (because the change in oslo::db can break unit tests for puppet-nova).

